channel.title: Logo creator needed?
channel.description: Okay, so I'm wanting to open a server thats called "darkside". Ive got most of it set up, but need to make a site for it. Before I do, I really need a good logo to go along with it. I dont know if this is where I should be posting this, so move it if needed. Anyways, so what I need in the logo is something that has to do with darth vader, or another prominent "darkside" figure. Colors are like black, white, and yellow. Have something that says "darkside" on it; and instead of a really serious looking star wars thing, something thats more on the 'pimp' side. If someone could do this for me, it would be GREATLY appreciated. Thanks.
